.Xr memcpy 3 ,
.Xr memmove 3 ,
.Xr memset 3
.Sh STANDARDS
The functions
.Fn memchr ,
.Fn memcmp ,
.Fn memcpy ,
.Fn memmove ,
and
.Fn memset
conform to
.St -isoC .
.Sh HISTORY
